326
00:20:27,143 --> 00:20:28,645
So when's the big day?

327
00:20:30,563 --> 00:20:32,148
Well, that is touchy.

328
00:20:32,232 --> 00:20:33,858
Don't be comin' to my house
to break bread,

329
