428
00:27:10,713 --> 00:27:11,923
You're smoking again...

429
00:27:12,006 --> 00:27:13,466
Smellin' my clothes now, Ma?

430
00:27:13,549 --> 00:27:15,259
We're all just things in your way.

431
00:27:15,343 --> 00:27:17,178
